---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';

const title = "Warehouse Line Striping Nixa MO | Industrial Safety Markings";
const description = "Warehouse floor markings, forklift lanes, and safety striping in Nixa, Missouri. We connect you with certified contractors experienced in high-traffic industrial and distribution center line striping across Christian County.";

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "LocalBusiness",
  "name": "Springfield Lot Striping",
  "description": "We connect property managers and facility owners with certified commercial parking lot striping contractors.",
  "serviceType": "Commercial Parking Lot Striping"
};

---

<BaseLayout {title} {description}>
  <Header />
  
  <div class="pt-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-primary-dark">Warehouse Line Striping in Nixa, Missouri</h1>
      <div class="text-brand-yellow text-xl mt-2">Safety-Focused • Durable • Industrial</div>
      
      <img src="/images/xai_grok-imagine-image_20260623_174834_8c90e1f0.jpg" alt="Warehouse line striping Nixa Missouri" class="my-12 rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full" />
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-concrete leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-xl">We connect Nixa facility managers and warehouse operators with certified contractors who specialize in warehouse floor markings, forklift lanes, pedestrian walkways, and industrial safety striping.</p>
        
        <p>Nixa has experienced strong growth in distribution, light manufacturing, and logistics facilities. These high-traffic environments require clear, durable markings that improve safety and operational efficiency while withstanding constant forklift and truck movement.</p>

        <h2>Why Warehouse Markings Matter in Nixa</h2>
        <p>Poorly marked warehouse floors create safety risks, slow down operations, and increase the chance of accidents or equipment damage. As Nixa continues to attract new industrial and logistics tenants, property owners are increasingly focused on maintaining clear, professional internal striping that supports daily operations.</p>
        
        <p>Our network includes contractors experienced in high-traffic industrial environments who understand how to select the right materials and application methods for long-lasting results.</p>

        <h2>Warehouse Striping Services</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Forklift lanes and pedestrian walkways</li>
          <li>Loading dock approach markings</li>
          <li>Storage zone and racking aisle identification</li>
          <li>Safety and hazard zone striping</li>
          <li>Directional and traffic flow markings</li>
          <li>High-durability paint and thermoplastic options</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Local Conditions in Christian County</h2>
        <p>Nixa-area warehouses often operate with high daily forklift traffic and frequent trailer movement. Standard parking lot paint frequently fails in these environments. We connect you with contractors who understand material selection and application techniques that hold up under heavy use.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-surface p-10 rounded-3xl my-12">
          <p class="italic">"We needed to re-stripe the entire warehouse floor after a layout change. The new markings have held up extremely well under constant forklift traffic. Very professional work."</p>
          <p class="mt-6 font-semibold">— Warehouse Manager, Nixa Distribution Center</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Need Warehouse Floor Markings in Nixa?</h2>
        <p>If your facility requires new or updated warehouse striping, we connect you with contractors who specialize in industrial and distribution center applications.</p>
        
        <p class="text-center my-12">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary text-xl px-14 py-6 inline-block">Request Warehouse Striping Quote →</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>